<section id="about" class="fade-in">
  <span class="sec-lbl" id="lAbout">About Gujarat</span>
  <h2 class="sec-title" id="aboutTitle">The Jewel of <em>Western India</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="aboutBody">Gujarat is India's westernmost state, a land where ancient wisdom meets modern enterprise. Birthplace of Mahatma Gandhi, Gujarat has shaped India's freedom struggle and continues to drive economic growth. From the sacred Statue of Unity and pristine coastal regions to the world's largest textile industry and diamond trading hubs, Gujarat embodies entrepreneurial spirit. Home to the Asiatic lion in the Gir Forest, magnificent temples, the white desert of Kutch, and vibrant business communities, Gujarat is where tradition dances with innovation. It's a state of pilgrims and traders, saints and entrepreneurs, ancient riches and contemporary success.</p>
</section>

<section id="weather" class="fade-in">
  <span class="sec-lbl" id="lWeather">Climate &amp; Best Time</span>
  <h2 class="sec-title" id="weatherTitle">When to Visit <em>Gujarat</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Gujarat experiences three main seasons: hot summers (March-May reaching 40°C+), moderate monsoons (June-September), and pleasant winters (November-February). Winter is the best time for most destinations.</p>
  <div class="wgrid" id="wGrid"></div>
</section>

<section id="districts" class="fade-in">
  <span class="sec-lbl" id="lDist">All 33 Districts</span>
  <h2 class="sec-title" id="distTitle">Every District of <em>Gujarat</em></h2>
  <p class="sec-body" id="distNote" style="margin-bottom:18px">Gujarat's 33 districts each offer unique cultural, economic, and natural attractions. From coastal pearl ports to inland diamond capitals, discover the diversity within this thriving state.</p>
  <input class="dsearch" type="text" id="distSearch" placeholder="Search districts..." oninput="filterDistricts(this.value)">
  <div class="dist-accordion" id="distAccordion"></div>
</section>

<section id="places" class="fade-in">
  <span class="sec-lbl" id="lPlaces">Sacred &amp; Historic Sites</span>
  <h2 class="sec-title" id="placesTitle">Wonders of <em>Gujarat</em></h2>
  <div class="pgrid" id="pGrid"></div>
</section>

<section id="arts" class="fade-in">
  <span class="sec-lbl" id="lArts">Arts, Crafts &amp; Heritage</span>
  <h2 class="sec-title" id="artsTitle">Living Traditions of <em>Gujarat</em></h2>
  <div class="agrid" id="artGrid"></div>
</section>

<section id="tradition" class="fade-in">
  <span class="sec-lbl" id="lTrad">Festivals &amp; Celebrations</span>
  <h2 class="sec-title" id="tradTitle">Soul of <em>Gujarati Culture</em></h2>
